Question: Some of the lemons in both images are cut.

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there any cut lemons in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there any cut lemons in the image?')

FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
